Package jason.asSyntax.patterns.goal

Class Summary
BC Implementation of the Blind Commitment pattern (see DALT 2006 paper)
BDG Implementation of the Backtracking Declarative Goal pattern (see DALT 2006 paper)
DG Implementation of the Declarative Goal pattern (see DALT 2006 paper)
EBDG Implementation of the Exclusive BDG pattern (see DALT 2006 paper)
MG Implementation of the Maintenance Goal pattern (see DALT 2006 paper)
OMC Implementation of the Open-Minded Commitment pattern (see DALT 2006 paper)
RC Implementation of the Relativised Commitment pattern (see DALT 2006 paper)
SGA Implementation of the Sequenced Goal Adoption pattern (see DALT 2006 paper)
SMC Implementation of the Single-Minded Commitment pattern (see DALT 2006 paper)
